---
title: Teriyaki-Style Chicken Stir-Fry with Sesame Broccoli & Jasmine Rice
description: Forget takeout: the path to sweet-spicy-savory dinner bliss is as simple as breaking out a frying pan! In this recipe, chicken is marinated in a tantalizing ponzu sauce. Tried-and-true steamed broccoli tossed with sesame seeds come together with the chicken over a bed of rice—in 30 minutes, no less! Now that’s a symphony of flavors and textures that are so delicious, you might just lick the plate.
